public class Jsr330BindingLocatorImpl
extends Object
implements Jsr330BindingLocator, BindingFactory

Default implementation for the Jsr330BindingLocator. It builds a list by first calling all Jsr330Bindings, and then finding individual Jsr330Binding(s) in the system.
